OL,5, The Greek prime minister has pledged to
OL,6, give tourists who had to escape the    
OL,7, recent wildfires on the island of      
OL,8, Rhodes a one-week holiday there for    
OL,9, free.                                  
OL,11,FSpeaking on ITV's Good Morning Britain,
OL,12,FKyriakos Mitsotakis said people could  
OL,13,Ftake up the offer in the spring or     
OL,14,Fautumn of 2024.                        
OL,16,FMore than 20,000 people were evacuated 
OL,17,Fwhen wildfires broke out in July.      
OL,19,FThousands of UK holidaymakers were     
OL,20,Fflown home to the UK.                  
